大多人類擁有23對（46條）染色體。當中第23對為性染色體<ref>[http://vega.sanger.ac.uk/Homo_sapiens/index.html Vega.sanger.ad.uk] {{Wayback|url=http://vega.sanger.ac.uk/Homo_sapiens/index.html |date=20060412174840 }}, all data in this table was derived from this database, 2008-11-11.</ref>，用以決定影響個體最終發育成雌性（XX）還是雄性（XY）<ref>{{cite book |last=Llord |first=J |first2=D |last2=Uchil |editor-first=Sabaratnam |editor-last=Arulkumaran |editor2-first=Lesley |editor2-last=Regan |editor3-first=Aris |editor3-last=Papageorghiou |editor4-first=Ash |editor4-last=Monga |editor5-first=David |editor5-last=Farquharson |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lRaWcRYx_7YC&pg=PP1 |chapter=12: Reproduction: Ambiguous Genitalia |title=Oxford Desk Reference: Obstetrics and Gynaecology |publisher=Oxford University Press |year=2011 |page=464 |access-date=2020-06-16 |archive-date=2016-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502024357/https://books.google.com/books?id=lRaWcRYx_7YC&pg=PP1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。卵子所攜帶的一般是X染色體；而精子則有一半機會攜帶Y染色體，另有一半攜帶X染色體<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.genderselectionauthority.com/blog/five-facts-about-xx-or-xy |website=www.genderselectionauthority.com |title=Five Facts about XX or XY |date=2014-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006160607/https://www.genderselectionauthority.com/blog/five-facts-about-xx-or-xy |archive-date=2016-10-06 |accessdate=2020-06-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，故此後代的性別將由男性方的精子決定<ref name="Harrison">{{Cite book|title = Harrison's Principles of Internal Medicine|url = https://archive.org/details/harrisonsprincip00asfa|last = Fauci|first = Anthony S.|publisher = McGraw-Hill Medical|year = 2008|isbn = 978-0-07-147693-5|location = |pages = [https://archive.org/details/harrisonsprincip00asfa/page/n2377 2339]–2346|edition = 17th|last2 = Braunwald|first2 = Eugene|last3 = Kasper|first3 = Dennis L.|last4 = Hauser|first4 = Stephen L.|last5 = Longo|first5 = Dan L.|last6 = Jameson|first6 = J. Larry|last7 = Loscalzo|first7 = Joseph}}</ref>。不過這也有可能產生性染色體不屬上述兩者的後代<ref name="Harrison"/>。

X或Y染色体特有的基因即為性连锁基因<ref>{{cite book|title=Introduction to Veterinary Anatomy and Physiology E-Book|author1=Victoria Aspinall|author2=Melanie Cappello|page=139|year=2009|isbn=9780702048593|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=z0uJmrn6qAMC&pg=PA139|access-date=2020-06-16|archive-date=2020-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616081256/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=z0uJmrn6qAMC&pg=PA139|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最常發生紅綠[[色盲|色盲]]的相關隱性遺傳基因位於X染色體上。男性只有一條X染色體，而女性則有兩條X染色體，缺失的基因可以由另一條補足，故此男性比女性容易有色盲<ref name=NEI2015>{{cite web|title=Facts About Color Blindness|url=https://nei.nih.gov/health/color_blindness/facts_about|website=NEI|accessdate=2016-07-29|date=2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728003639/https://nei.nih.gov/health/color_blindness/facts_about|archivedate=2016-07-28}}</ref>。 

人類的[[XY性别决定系统|XY系统]]並非世上唯一的性别決定系统。鳥類的情況跟人類相反，牠們以ZW系統決定性別—— ZZ為雄性，ZW為雌性<ref>{{cite book| first1= Maria | last1= Lepowsky | first2= JS | last2= Chafetz | title= The Encyclopedic Entry of Gender | via = Reference.com; Dictionary.com| year= 2008| isbn= }}}</ref>。人類尚不了解是否全部鳥類都是由雌性或雄性方的配子決定性别。已知有几种蝴蝶的後代性別由雌性方的配子決定<ref>{{cite journal|last2= Sahara|first2=K.|last3=Marec|first3=F.|year= 2007|title=Sex Chromosomes and Sex Determination in Lepidoptera|journal=Sexual Development|volume=1|issue=6|pages=332–46|doi=10.1159/000111765|pmid=18391545|quote=The speciose insect order Lepidoptera (moths and butterflies) and their closest relatives, Trichoptera (caddis flies), share a female-heterogametic sex chromosome system|last1=Traut|first1=W.}}</ref>。

[[鸭嘴兽|鸭嘴兽]]的性別決定系統較為混合複雜，雄性鸭嘴兽有十條性染色體，XY各佔一半<ref name="discoverPlatypus">{{Cite web|url=http://discovermagazine.com/2005/apr/sex-ys-platypuses0425/|title=Sex, Ys, and Platypuses|publisher=Discover|author=Selim, Jocelyn|date=2005-04-25|accessdate=2008-05-07|archive-date=2008-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516233225/http://discovermagazine.com/2005/apr/sex-ys-platypuses0425|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
